php-goat1000-svggraph (0.1.1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix PHP 8+ strict type errors in string functions across the library:
    - Graph.php: str_replace() on non-string tooltip value
    - Text.php: strlen()/strpos()/htmlspecialchars() on non-string text
    - Coords.php: substr()/strtolower() on numeric coordinates
    - GradientList.php: strlen()/str_contains() on numeric colour values
    - ColourGroup.php: strpos() on non-string stroke colour
    - Number.php: exception message for non-scalar values

